產者，為竊盜\r\n罪，處五年以下有期徒刑、拘役或五十萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/111%2c%e5%af%a9%e7%b0%a1%2c35%2c20220215%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,111,審簡,35,20220215,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"審簡","JNO":"35","JDATE":"20220215","JTITLE":"竊盜"}